{"tid":1428593,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我係度祝所有藍屍子子孫孫都讀唔到大學","createTime":"2019-08-07T10:20:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T16:03:56.000Z","uid":243255,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"36d694bcafbeedbdc9ba48f899636eaccfa8df80","tid":1428593,"uid":243255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:20:04.000Z","msg":"我見D人成日話黃絲好暴力, 大學生好暴力收左錢先去衝, 應該和平示威, 唔應該阻大家返工<br />\n<br />\n我係度真心誠懇祝所有藍屍子子孫孫讀唔到大學<br />\n以免讀書讀壞腦 去進行暴力行為,支持反送中活動<br />\n<br />\n藍屍子孫們應該要好好學長輩, 盡早進入勞動市場<br />\n學長輩準時返工 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91ecba6e350222def545990ba869e2d8d9054270","tid":1428593,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:22:38.000Z","msg":"[形象工程] 我們不是暴徒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1428424\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1428424</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"65bb8d092e8422c8dfe376e2c09e08b48ea37810","tid":1428593,"uid":284878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:24:21.000Z","msg":"大學生表示我阿婆係民智未開嘅深藍<br />\n講到口乾都改變唔到佢"},{"pid":"4bc9bbddcbc14a34ea81a418788335c7db1698f5","tid":1428593,"uid":224510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:25:26.000Z","msg":"佢哋興買學歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"befec1919945dadb4e03df4a64a250dc16afc0bc","tid":1428593,"uid":264956,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:25:32.000Z","msg":"長輩細個時叫你讀多d書, 讀好d書要入大學, 而家就話讀大學讀屎片, 教壞人係廢青, 仲話係老師有問題, 真係思覺失調!"},{"pid":"3d4e5ad2329abaafaa6b8f8d49494d34c8e8ea2c","tid":1428593,"uid":243255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:32:39.000Z","msg":"比多D祝福佢地啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgm